data.description: ** UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACK UP OFFERS ** PRICE IMPROVED!! This newer construction 3 bedroom, two bathroom home sits on a corner lot that is just over half an acre. It has beautiful hickory cabinetry and framework throughout the entire house. The over sized garage offers plenty of room for work benches and toy or vehicle storage. Plenty of space inside and out, this floor plan offers ample room to live and entertain. There is extra insulation throughout the home to make heating and cooling easy. This home is within close proximity of Deer Point Lake, public parks, and multiple boat ramps, you'll have access to enjoy what beautiful Northern Bay County has to offer. Quality built by a LOCAL contractor, energy efficient and ready for its next owner. Just 24 miles from Tyndall Air Force Base and approximately 25 miles from the worlds most beautiful beaches. Get all the conveniences of being a short commute to town while still being able to easily experience the beauty of Northern Bay County. Bring your boat, toys or other recreational vehicles as there is plenty of room to store them! Call a REALTOR today to schedule a private tour of this beautiful home! If important please verify information.
